two chemicals that have never

00:01:43.620 --> 00:01:46.020 align:middle line:90%
necessarily been mixed before.

00:01:46.020 --> 00:01:49.080 align:middle line:84%
And if those chemicals
haven't been mixed before,

00:01:49.080 --> 00:01:51.780 align:middle line:84%
